{"tid":1147133,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple watch 維修錶帶DIY","createTime":"2019-05-09T16:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T00:00:13.000Z","uid":80396,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96a87c4f78deb9c187905bba92e9d29f0118fd47","tid":1147133,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:26:04.000Z","msg":"話說隻Apple watch條錶帶都黃哂，於是去買隻99蚊既膠皮錶帶<br />\n點知用左一日，個插頭就已經甩左。把心一橫，換條普通錶用既真皮帶落去好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.拆埋未壞既果邊出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHWFRDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHWFRDV.jpg&h=e65a718b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.用2mm銅支屈番個U字出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2V8EnL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2V8EnL7.jpg&h=7bd3b78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.鋸甩佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkTdsdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkTdsdc.jpg&h=364c5f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.將U字銅支放落原本既錶帶插入面，同松香清潔焊接地方，再焊實佢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKyAFy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKyAFy2.jpg&h=765a31d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n注意兩邊材料唔同，插頭要比銅條熱，錫先個浸哂成個駁位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X1B9sZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X1B9sZ.jpg&h=063e69ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.打磨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enPgp1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenPgp1D.jpg&h=8e95c7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.最治愈既一步。因為一件工件淨係用沙紙磨，磨極都唔會有光澤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAJkRHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAJkRHc.jpg&h=682b0bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候就要用研磨膏去拋光(原理就好似刷牙，牙膏就好似膏狀既幼沙紙，磨令棚牙)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F66ZnPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF66ZnPw.jpg&h=31b5c115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗你都睇到個分別了。<br />\n<br />\n7.今次條錶帶係比你中間打條軸心去裝落隻錶，但因為我係同落Apple watch,連結隻錶係一個口字型，亦唔可以裝好錶帶再燒焊，因為會燒爛。所以就要拆線裝了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRLGBaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRLGBaw.jpg&h=5e799a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做完收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pD4zWaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpD4zWaO.jpg&h=292a233b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入番落袋再開左次箱，呃下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rhz4yXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhz4yXY.jpg&h=185a4601&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4772ff0b1f3c572400159daea71c0e43a1a78966","tid":1147133,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d55781b6ec1262a7368f02c06999d7a5bb94521","tid":1147133,"uid":161274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:33:06.000Z","msg":"最鍾意睇人DIY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd0de427794370ecfb1f20b4ccf3df534ba5698","tid":1147133,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"「呃下自己」笑咗"},{"pid":"7bfd35e380621062278e4b3c8b5c117257864f95","tid":1147133,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"e431108fadcf194b5e56c7ebe926b16af5ab3764","tid":1147133,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"有無上手圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae82f386ccfe51d222453d4fadcd2df8bc484e1","tid":1147133,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd0de427794370ecfb1f20b4ccf3df534ba5698","tid":1147133,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"「呃下自己」笑咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"我都係比人呃，點知會一日就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f0fb02b900527f563286f7a02b7d0ccd35b568","tid":1147133,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}